dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents supervisory districts for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2007. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office on November 30, 2007.[This dataset is of the Supervisor Districts for Dane County, Wisconsin. The data was originally developed by the Dane County Regional Planning Commission, Dane County Board Office, Dane County Department of Planning and Development and the Dane County Board. Updates to the district boundaries were done by the Dane County Land Information Office following County Board approval.]
